::Prowl::

An exciting feeling runs through Prowl as Iron Raptor touches his shoulder. 
He frowns. Why was he reacting like this? He shakes his head to clear it.

"Ok. See you at the base," he says, walks back to Zenyak, and transforms into 
beast mode. Grabbing Zenyak in his talons, he flies off toward the Ark.
